songs.title: Tittli
songs.lyrics:
[Hook (x2)]
Tittli, nazuk kalaiyan
Tikhe-tikhe naksh tere tittli
Nazuk kalaiyan
Morni de raks tere, tittli

[Verse 1]
Sanwli, ni patli jiven
Tittli enhi sohni
Jihdi koi hadd nahi
Tere ton vadh nahi
Kurhiyan ch koi hor kurhi
Tu kise ton ghat nahi
Koi na tere vargi honi
Ehde ‘ch koi shaq nahi
Mera tere te hakk nahi
Par main jannda va tu ki chaye
Armaan tere nazar aan
Jo tu akhian ‘ch kajle naal chupaye

[Hook (x2)]
Tittli, nazuk kalaiyan
Tikhe-tikhe naksh tere tittli
Nazuk kalaiyan
Morni de raks tere, tittli

[Verse 2]
Sohniye di nazuk kalaiyan
Ankhiyan di gehraiyan
Zulfan samundra ‘ch
Lehran jive aaian
Dindiyan gawahiyan
Tasveera je lave
Jadon bebas angdaiyan
Palkan teri akhiyan
Te badlan wangu chaiyan
Mainu ginvave beparwahiyan
Kehndi iss waari teri jit nahi

[Hook (x2)]
Tittli, nazuk kalaiyan
Tikhe-tikhe naksh tere tittli
Nazuk kalaiyan
Morni de raks tere, tittli

[Outro (x3)]
Remains of the ones rap star
Remains of the ones rap star
Remains of the ones rap star
